IDENTITY AND ACCESS MANAGEMENT,IAM Access Control and Permission Management,Sub-system: Keycloak,Keycloak provides a comprehensive Identity and Access Management solution, supporting IAM by offering features like user federation, identity brokering, and social login. Keycloak's REST API extension module facilitates custom management of access controls and permissions, integrating seamlessly with various user authentication and authorization mechanisms.,docs/en/modules/arch/pages/architecture/platform-api/services/keycloak-rest-api-ext.adoc